.TH "CITADEL" "1" "Jul 2026" "AceTeam" "Citadel CLI Manual"

.SH NAME
citadel-update-install - Download and install the latest version


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcitadel update install [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Downloads the latest version from GitHub, verifies the checksum,
backs up the current version, and installs the new binary.

.PP
If the new version fails to start, it will automatically roll back
to the previous version.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for install


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--debug\fP[=false]
	Enable debug output

.PP
\fB--no-color\fP[=false]
	Disable colorized output


.SH SEE ALSO
\fBcitadel-update(1)\fP
